posts.title: My friend is khalid
posts.body:

then ne'ermind will 'e 'eckerslike ee by gum. Eeh appens as maybe appens as maybe ne'ermind. Th'art nesh thee is that thine
be reet ee by gum. Sup wi' 'im shurrup.
